## Remember

1. **Design Tokens First** - Always import Colors, Spacing, Typography
2. **Reuse Components** - Don't recreate buttons, cards, inputs
3. **Keep Screens Simple** - Screens should just assemble components
4. **No Hardcoded Values** - Always use tokens (Colors.*, Spacing.*, Typography.*)
5. **Follow the Hierarchy** - Tokens â†’ Base Components â†’ Feature Components â†’ Screens

